SUBJECT 2: The most
common reaction

00:02:48.870 --> 00:02:50.995
I get when I'm on a flight
sitting next to somebody

00:02:50.995 --> 00:02:52.970
and they ask what do I
do, and I tell them I

00:02:52.970 --> 00:02:54.370
study sleeping sloths
and I climb trees,

00:02:54.370 --> 00:02:55.370
they think it's a joke.

00:02:55.370 --> 00:02:56.840
And then I tell them
no, I'm serious,

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:58.381
